WEBVTT

00:01.772 --> 00:03.404
Emily:
 MY FATHER WAS AN INNOCENT MAN

00:03.404 --> 00:04.735
DESTROYED BY POWERFUL PEOPLE.

00:04.735 --> 00:06.777
THE GRAYSONS ARE BEHIND THIS,
AND THEY'RE GONNA PAY.

00:06.777 --> 00:09.710
I'VE DEDICATED MY LIFE
 TO AVENGING HIS DEATH...

00:09.710 --> 00:11.542
EVENTUALLY, SOMEONE'S
GONNA FIND YOU OUT.

00:11.542 --> 00:15.186
...AND I WON'T STOP UNTIL
 THEY'VE ALL PAID THE PRICE.

00:15.186 --> 00:17.288
WHERE AM I?
 GRAYSON MANOR, OF COURSE.

00:17.288 --> 00:19.150
YOU'RE
TAKEDA'S DAUGHTER.
 NIKO.

00:19.150 --> 00:20.491
I'M NOT SUPPOSED TO BE HERE.

00:20.491 --> 00:22.123
I SHOULD BE AWAY WITH AIDEN,
WITH HIS RING ON MY FINGER,

00:22.123 --> 00:24.295
NOT DANIEL'S.
 YOU AND AIDEN ARE ENGAGED?

00:24.295 --> 00:26.657
AND EMILY, OBVIOUSLY, DOESN'T
KNOW ABOUT US -- OUR PAST.

00:26.657 --> 00:28.559
Victoria:
BECAUSE OF THE SURGERIES
REQUIRED TO SAVE YOUR LIFE,

00:28.559 --> 00:30.331
YOU'LL NEVER
BE ABLE TO CONCEIVE.

00:30.331 --> 00:32.262
Daniel: EMILY LIED
ABOUT THE PREGNANCY.

00:32.262 --> 00:33.634
SHE MADE IT UP
TO SCARE YOU AWAY.

00:33.634 --> 00:35.206
ARE YOU ENDING THIS
WITH ME?

00:35.206 --> 00:37.538
Emily: THERE HAS BEEN MUCH
SPECULATION AS TO WHO SHOT ME,

00:37.538 --> 00:39.170
IT WAS LYDIA DAVIS.

00:39.170 --> 00:41.172
I KNOW IT WAS YOU,
DANIEL.

00:41.172 --> 00:43.244
EMILY CEMENTED LYDIA'S FATE
AND SAVED YOURS.

00:43.244 --> 00:45.216
I'M NOT GOING ANYWHERE.

00:46.677 --> 00:48.519
WHEN I WAS A CHILD,

00:48.519 --> 00:52.483
MY FATHER WOKE ME EVERY MORNING
 WITH THE SAME PHRASE --

00:52.483 --> 00:55.156
"LIFE IS A GREAT SUNRISE."

00:55.156 --> 00:59.430
THE WORDS SHAPED
 THE WAY I SAW THE DAWN.

00:59.430 --> 01:03.063
BUT AFTER MY FATHER
 WAS TAKEN FROM ME,

01:03.063 --> 01:06.237
THE MORNING SUN
 BURNED LIKE FIRE.

01:06.237 --> 01:10.171
THAT'S WHEN I LEARNED
 WHAT HATRED WAS

01:10.171 --> 01:13.244
AND THAT IT WOULD GREET ME
 EACH DAY TO COME.

01:23.254 --> 01:25.256
[ GASPS ]

01:26.617 --> 01:29.620
YOU PULLED YOUR STITCHES OUT
IN YOUR SLEEP.

01:30.791 --> 01:33.093
THANK YOU
FOR COMING SO QUICKLY.

01:33.093 --> 01:36.467
MY FATHER WOULD HAVE WANTED ME
TO HELP HIS FAVORITE DISCIPLE.

01:36.467 --> 01:38.829
NOT PUNCH YOU
IN THE STOMACH

01:38.829 --> 01:40.831
AND STORM OUT OF HERE
LIKE I DID LAST WEEK.

01:40.831 --> 01:42.803
I'M GLAD YOU DID.

01:42.803 --> 01:45.676
YOU HELPED ME RECOMMIT
TO TAKEDA'S TEACHINGS.

01:45.676 --> 01:48.609
WELL, LET'S GET YOU
STITCHED UP.

01:48.609 --> 01:51.182
I'VE DECIDED
ON A QUICKER FIX.

01:58.289 --> 02:00.691
YOU CALLED ME HERE
TO CAUTERIZE YOU?

02:00.691 --> 02:02.393
THAT'S INSANE.
I'M NOT DOING IT.

02:02.393 --> 02:05.196
DO YOU KNOW
WHAT ORPHANS DREAM OF

02:05.196 --> 02:08.199
WHEN THEY STOP WISHING
FOR THEIR PARENTS TO RETURN?

02:09.199 --> 02:11.302
WE THINK ABOUT
FILLING THE EMPTINESS

02:11.302 --> 02:13.804
WITH FAMILIES OF OUR OWN.

02:15.306 --> 02:18.209
THANKS TO DANIEL,
THAT HOPE IS GONE FOR ME.

02:22.673 --> 02:26.217
THIS DOESN'T MEAN YOU'RE READY
FOR A SPARRING MATCH.

02:26.217 --> 02:27.778
WHEN YOU RESUME
PHYSICAL ACTIVITY,

02:27.778 --> 02:30.181
YOU HAVE TO DO IT SLOWLY.

02:30.181 --> 02:32.723
THEN I'LL START
WITH MIND GAMES.

02:33.784 --> 02:36.857
FIRST THINGS FIRST, YOU NEED
SOMETHING TO BITE DOWN ON.

02:36.857 --> 02:38.729
JUST DO IT.

02:44.164 --> 02:46.166
[ SCOFFS ]

02:49.740 --> 02:51.742
[ SIGHS ]

02:54.945 --> 02:56.377
WELCOME TO RECKONING DAY.

02:56.377 --> 03:00.511
NO NEED TO FURROW
THAT HANDSOME BROW.

03:00.511 --> 03:03.814
I'M NOT HERE
WITH THE POLICE...

03:03.814 --> 03:05.816
THOUGH I SHOULD BE.

03:05.816 --> 03:07.818
NOLAN, I CAN'T BEGIN
TO TELL YOU HOW SORRY I AM.

03:07.818 --> 03:11.662
WE ARE A MILLION MILES
PAST SORRY.

03:11.662 --> 03:13.664
YOU ASSAULTED ME.

03:13.664 --> 03:15.666
YOU STOLE FROM ME...

03:15.666 --> 03:18.769
ALL TO WIN FAVOR
WITH YOUR MOTHER?

03:20.531 --> 03:24.204
THERE'S SOMETHING TWISTED
ABOUT YOU. YOU'RE SICK.

03:24.204 --> 03:25.576
STOP.

03:27.278 --> 03:29.480
WHY ARE YOU HERE?

03:29.480 --> 03:33.484
I KNOW THAT
YOU'RE DESPERATE

03:33.484 --> 03:36.987
FOR ANSWERS
ABOUT HOW YOU CAME TO BE,

03:36.987 --> 03:39.219
AND...

03:39.219 --> 03:42.423
I KNOW THAT VICTORIA
HASN'T BEEN FORTHCOMING.

03:42.423 --> 03:48.829
SO...THIS IS
A POLICE REPORT FROM 1974.

03:48.829 --> 03:53.964
I DUG IT UP LAST YEAR
WHEN VICKY G. ENLISTED ME

03:53.964 --> 03:56.967
TO HELP HER FIND
HER LONG-LOST SON.

03:56.967 --> 04:00.811
YOU SEE, ACCORDING TO THIS,
SOMEONE ELSE WAS SEARCHING

04:00.811 --> 04:03.974
FOR LITTLE PATRICK OSBOURNE,
AS WELL.

04:09.249 --> 04:12.022
DEREK.
 VICTORIA.

04:12.022 --> 04:14.955
I WAS TOLD
YOU WOULDN'T BE HERE.

04:14.955 --> 04:16.627
OH, THIS IS
COMPLETELY MY FAULT.

04:16.627 --> 04:18.629
DR. ROBINSON ONLY AGREED
ON A HOUSE CALL

04:18.629 --> 04:21.591
BECAUSE I FELT TOO WEAK
TO GET TO HIS OFFICE.

04:21.591 --> 04:25.636
I THOUGHT THAT YOU'D BE AT YOUR
MORNING TENNIS GAME, VICTORIA.

04:25.636 --> 04:28.268
MY DOUBLES PARTNER
MYSTERIOUSLY CANCELLED.

04:28.268 --> 04:30.941
[ INHALES SHARPLY ]
WELL, THIS IS AWKWARD.
 YEAH.

04:30.941 --> 04:32.943
IF YOU'LL EXCUSE ME,
LADIES.

04:32.943 --> 04:34.905
THANK YOU.

04:34.905 --> 04:37.708
[ DOOR OPENS AND CLOSES ]

04:37.708 --> 04:40.050
HOW LONG HAVE YOU BEEN
SEEING MY THERAPIST?

04:40.050 --> 04:41.912
JUST TODAY.
 MM.

04:41.912 --> 04:45.055
CHARLOTTE MENTIONED HOW
HELPFUL HE WAS IN BRINGING
YOU TWO BACK TOGETHER

04:45.055 --> 04:47.758
AFTER SHE LEARNED THAT
DAVID CLARKE WAS HER FATHER.

04:47.758 --> 04:50.491
IF YOU'RE TRYING TO BUILD
A BRIDGE BETWEEN US, EMILY,

04:50.491 --> 04:53.464
HERE'S A TIP -- STAY ON
YOUR SIDE OF THE RIVER.

04:53.464 --> 04:56.867
DR. ROBINSON WARNED ME
YOU MAY FEEL THIS WAY...

04:56.867 --> 04:59.930
AND THAT DANIEL
MIGHT BE RESISTANT, TOO.

04:59.930 --> 05:01.832
RESISTANT?
[ CHUCKLES ]

05:01.832 --> 05:04.435
HE HASN'T LAID EYES
ON YOU IN DAYS.

05:04.435 --> 05:06.076
HIS QUARTERS
ARE SO FAR AWAY,

05:06.076 --> 05:08.839
HE MAY AS WELL BE
SLEEPING IN THE STABLES.

05:08.839 --> 05:11.782
WELL, I GUESS WE'LL JUST
HAVE TO GIVE IT TIME, THEN.

05:13.313 --> 05:16.086
ARE YOU SURE YOU DON'T MIND
ALWAYS SLEEPING AT MY PLACE?

05:16.086 --> 05:18.088
OH, I LIKE
YOUR APARTMENT.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

05:18.088 --> 05:20.090
IT'S COZY.

05:20.090 --> 05:22.322
I GREW UP
IN DRAFTY CHATEAUS SO BIG,

05:22.322 --> 05:24.625
I NEVER KNEW WHERE
MY PARENTS OR BROTHERS WERE.

05:24.625 --> 05:26.727
I LOVE OPENING MY EYES
IN THE MORNING

05:26.727 --> 05:28.659
AND SEEING YOU
AND CARL SO CLOSE.

05:28.659 --> 05:30.861
THAT'S WHAT
MAKES IT A HOME.

05:32.863 --> 05:35.566
[ BOTH CHUCKLE ]

05:38.338 --> 05:39.770
OOH,
IT'S THERE!

05:39.770 --> 05:41.812
AHH.
 [ CHUCKLES ]

05:41.812 --> 05:43.714
[ CHUCKLES ]
HEY, BOBBY.

05:43.714 --> 05:47.077
GOOD TO SEE YOU, MAN.
COULD YOU DO ME A FAVOR?

05:48.348 --> 05:50.350
WOULD YOU KEEP THOSE
FRONT-ROW-CENTER THIS WEEK?

05:50.350 --> 05:52.122
IT'S THE LADY'S
PRIDE AND JOY.
 SURE.

05:52.122 --> 05:54.785
THE STAFF DID
SUCH A GOOD JOB.

05:57.087 --> 05:58.759
YEAH.
 WAIT.

05:58.759 --> 06:01.091
I DID NOT WRITE THIS.

06:01.091 --> 06:02.763
THE BY-LINE
SAYS YOU DID.

06:02.763 --> 06:05.836
NO, NO, I-I MEAN, YES, I DID,
BUT NOT WITH THOSE WORDS.

06:05.836 --> 06:07.638
NO, I MUST
GET TO THE OFFICE.

06:07.638 --> 06:09.440
SOMEONE'S HEAD
IS GOING TO ROLL.

06:13.404 --> 06:15.506
OH.

06:15.506 --> 06:17.147
ARE YOU HERE
TO ESCORT ME OUT?

06:17.147 --> 06:20.851
HOW APT THAT THE WOMAN
WHO LEFT ME WITHOUT AN ALLY

06:20.851 --> 06:23.153
IN THIS FAMILY CONFLICT
SHOULD SHOW ME THE DOOR.

06:23.153 --> 06:25.115
YOU'RE MOVING OUT?

06:25.115 --> 06:27.387
I'M SORRY. I DIDN'T
KNOW YOU WERE LEAVING.

06:27.387 --> 06:31.892
WELL, TRUTH BE TOLD, I'M ELATED,
LIKE A PRISONER PAROLED.

06:31.892 --> 06:34.094
BUT RATHER
THAN SHUFFLING OFF

06:34.094 --> 06:36.026
WITH A PLASTIC BAG
OF PERSONAL EFFECTS,

06:36.026 --> 06:38.429
I'M TAKING
MY FIRST EDITIONS.

06:38.429 --> 06:39.970
CONRAD, I --
I'D LIKE TO EXPLAIN MYSELF.

06:39.970 --> 06:41.772
YEAH?
WHAT'S TO EXPLAIN?

06:41.772 --> 06:44.975
WHEN YOU HELD THAT NEWS
CONFERENCE AND YOU THREW
LYDIA UNDER THE BUS,

06:44.975 --> 06:47.508
YOU DESTROYED
MY LAST CHANCE AT HAPPINESS.

06:47.508 --> 06:50.180
I HAD TO PROTECT
MY OWN CHANCE AT HAPPINESS.

06:50.180 --> 06:52.182
I WON'T LOSE DANIEL.

06:52.182 --> 06:54.044
[ CHUCKLES ]

06:54.044 --> 06:56.817
"TAMERLANE"
BY EDGAR ALLAN POE.

06:56.817 --> 06:59.850
THIS IS ONE OF THE VERY FEW
COPIES LEFT IN EXISTENCE.

06:59.850 --> 07:03.193
IN THE POEM, A WARLORD
REACHES THE CONCLUSION

07:03.193 --> 07:06.056
THAT LOVE IS
MORE FULFILLING THAN POWER.

07:07.057 --> 07:08.459
WHAT A FOOL.

07:08.459 --> 07:12.633
WHEN YOUR PARAMOUR
BETRAYS YOU, AS DANIEL WILL,

07:12.633 --> 07:15.766
COME FIND ME
AT THE SOUTHFORK.

07:15.766 --> 07:18.609
I'LL BE RUNNING MY WARTIME
OPERATIONS FROM THERE.

07:19.610 --> 07:20.941
THAT'S FOR YOU TO KEEP.

07:22.172 --> 07:23.974
MRS. GRAYSON,

07:23.974 --> 07:26.116
MS. LeMARCHAL'S
CALLING FOR DANIEL.

07:26.116 --> 07:29.049
SHE SAID IT'S URGENT.
SHOULD I WAKE HIM?

07:29.049 --> 07:31.852
THAT'S HIS WIFE'S JOB.

07:32.823 --> 07:34.154
DANIEL?

07:34.154 --> 07:37.157
MARGAUX CALLED.
THERE'S A CRISIS AT WORK.

07:38.789 --> 07:41.061
WE CAN'T AVOID
EACH OTHER FOREVER.

07:41.061 --> 07:43.163
LET'S TALK.

07:43.163 --> 07:45.666
Daniel:
ALL RIGHT, COME IN.

07:49.940 --> 07:53.143
WHAT DO YOU WANT TO
CHAT ABOUT? THE WEATHER?

07:53.143 --> 07:55.676
HOW I SLEPT LAST NIGHT?

07:55.676 --> 07:59.079
'CAUSE I DIDN'T.
NOT MUCH, ANYWAY.

08:00.210 --> 08:02.553
THAT ABOUT DOES IT FOR ME.

08:02.553 --> 08:05.055
WHAT'S NEW WITH YOU?

08:31.642 --> 08:33.914
I'D LOVE TO GO
TO AUNT GINA'S JEWELRY PARTY.

08:33.914 --> 08:36.647
JUST, THE THING IS,
WORK HAS ME SLAMMED RIGHT NOW.

08:36.647 --> 08:38.619
MA, PLEASE DON'T SAY
I'M BLOWING YOU OFF.

08:38.619 --> 08:40.049
I...

08:41.051 --> 08:42.623
UH, LOOK,
I'VE GOT TO HOP.

08:42.623 --> 08:44.695
A CUSTOMER'S GIVING
ME THE STINK-EYE.

08:44.695 --> 08:46.096
YEAH.

08:46.096 --> 08:48.759
IT'S ONE THING
TO DELIVER A WAKE-UP CALL

08:48.759 --> 08:51.201
TO MY HUSBAND
AND HIS MISTRESS,

08:51.201 --> 08:53.864
BUT I HAVE TOO MUCH
SELF-RESPECT TO WATCH
YOU LOUNGE BY OUR POOL.

08:53.864 --> 08:55.766
YOU HAVE TO GO NOW.

08:55.766 --> 08:59.269
WELL, DANIEL ASKED ME TO STAY,
AND I'M STICKING BY HIM.

08:59.269 --> 09:02.242
I WON'T LET YOU
DESTROY MY MARRIAGE.

09:02.242 --> 09:04.314
DON'T YOU THINK
THIS IS SAD, EMILY?

09:04.314 --> 09:07.217
FOR YOU, I MEAN.
HE DOESN'T LOVE YOU.

09:07.217 --> 09:09.980
OH, THAT'S
A CHEAP SHOT, SARA.

09:09.980 --> 09:13.253
I'M TRYING TO HANDLE
THIS WITH DIGNITY.

09:13.253 --> 09:15.586
AFTER PULLING
THE MOST PATHETIC STUNT EVER?

09:15.586 --> 09:18.258
FAKING A PREGNANCY
TO LOCK A GUY DOWN.

09:18.258 --> 09:20.260
DANIEL'S PUSHING
HIS BOUNDARIES WITH ME.

09:20.260 --> 09:23.864
AND AFTER THE PAIN I CAUSED,
IT'S UNDERSTANDABLE.

09:23.864 --> 09:27.267
RIGHT NOW YOUR EARTHINESS
IS WHAT'S CATCHING HIS EYE,

09:27.267 --> 09:30.741
BUT YOU DON'T
FIT IN HERE.
 I'M ACTUALLY
PROUD OF THAT.

09:30.741 --> 09:34.274
UNTIL PEOPLE FIND OUT ABOUT YOU
AND START JUDGING HIM.

09:34.274 --> 09:37.247
BECAUSE I'M TRASH?
IS THAT WHAT YOU'RE SAYING?

09:44.084 --> 09:45.986
EXCUSE ME.

09:45.986 --> 09:48.659
A GLASS OF CRISTAL, PLEASE.
 Man: RIGHT AWAY.

09:56.296 --> 09:59.169
AIDEN, I AM FINE
WITH YOU LIVING HERE

09:59.169 --> 10:01.371
AND I'VE EVEN GROWN
TO ENJOY

10:01.371 --> 10:04.104
OUR KILLER-AND-THE-TECH-WIZ
"ODD COUPLE" DYNAMIC.

10:04.104 --> 10:06.837
BUT YOU HAVE A LOT OF
NERVE INVITING A PERFECT
STRANGER TO CRASH HERE, TOO.

10:06.837 --> 10:09.609
SLOW DOWN, FELIX. I DON'T KNOW
WHAT YOU'RE TALKING ABOUT.

10:09.609 --> 10:13.183
THEN GO CHECK WITH
YOUR NEW ROOMIE, ROOMIE.

10:15.385 --> 10:17.848
I THOUGHT YOU WERE STAYING
AT YOUR FATHER'S LOFT.

10:17.848 --> 10:20.090
Niko: YOU MEAN THE PLACE
WHERE HE WAS MURDERED?

10:20.090 --> 10:22.222
I CAN'T SLEEP THERE.
IT GIVES ME NIGHTMARES.

10:22.222 --> 10:25.125
SO, WHEN EMILY CALLED
THIS MORNING TO ASK ME FOR HELP

10:25.125 --> 10:27.327
WITH HER WOUND CARE,
I DECIDED TO PACK UP MY THINGS.

10:27.327 --> 10:30.400
AND MAKE YOURSELF
AT HOME HERE.
 YEAH, IT'LL BE NICE.

10:32.162 --> 10:33.704
SO, YOU --
YOU ATTENDED TO EMILY.

10:33.704 --> 10:36.006
WHAT'S THE NEWS?
 PHYSICALLY,
SHE'S GONNA BE FINE.

10:36.006 --> 10:39.009
I THINK IT WAS FINDING
OUT SHE CAN'T HAVE CHILDREN
THAT HIT HER THE HARDEST.

10:39.009 --> 10:40.911
I CAN'T IMAGINE
SHE OPENED UP TO YOU.

10:40.911 --> 10:43.343
SHE...DOESN'T REALLY
DO THAT TO STRANGERS.

10:43.343 --> 10:45.215
SHE HAS TO ME.

10:45.215 --> 10:47.147
WE'VE SPOKEN
ABOUT ALL SORTS OF THINGS.

10:47.147 --> 10:50.320
DOES SHE KNOW ABOUT US?
 AS IN HOW WE'RE
BACK TOGETHER, YOU MEAN?

10:52.152 --> 10:53.984
NO.

10:53.984 --> 10:57.027
IF I TOLD HER THAT,
I'D JUST BE BRAGGING.

10:57.027 --> 11:00.330
I THOUGHT I COULD AVENGE
MY FATHER'S DEATH BY
MYSELF, BUT I CAN'T.

11:02.232 --> 11:04.234
I NEED YOU TO HELP ME.

11:10.871 --> 11:12.743
WHAT'S THE PROBLEM?

11:12.743 --> 11:14.374
HE WAS YOUR MENTOR.

11:20.110 --> 11:22.112
WHICH IS WHY I'M IN.

11:22.112 --> 11:24.414
♪♪♪

11:24.414 --> 11:28.258
"AWARE OF THE BAD BLOOD
BETWEEN THORNE AND LYDIA DAVIS,

11:28.258 --> 11:31.161
"CONRAD GRAYSON
TOOK THE PRE-MEDITATED STEP

11:31.161 --> 11:33.323
"OF BUYING
HIS MISTRESS A HANDGUN

11:33.323 --> 11:36.026
AND WELCOMING HER ABOARD
THE HONEYMOON YACHT."

11:36.026 --> 11:39.299
THAT SENTENCE DID NOT
EXIST WHEN I SIGNED
OFF ON THE FINAL COPY.

11:39.299 --> 11:43.073
THE LAST PERSON TO HANDLE
THE BOOK WAS MY ASSISTANT
EDITOR, JESSICA ROCHE.

11:43.073 --> 11:45.335
SHE'S RESPONSIBLE.
 YEAH, WELL,
GET HER ASS IN HERE.

11:45.335 --> 11:47.407
SHE'S GONE -- SUDDENLY
PICKED UP AND MOVED TO EUROPE.

11:47.407 --> 11:50.410
SHE SABOTAGED US, DANIEL, AND
BELIEVE ME, WHEN I FIND HER --

11:50.410 --> 11:53.113
MARGAUX LeMARCHAL?
 OUI?

11:55.285 --> 11:57.217
MERCI.

11:59.019 --> 12:00.320
OH, GREAT.

12:00.320 --> 12:03.954
CONRAD IS SUING VOULEZ
 FOR LIBEL. [ SCOFFS ]

12:03.954 --> 12:06.256
[ SIGHS ]

12:06.256 --> 12:09.099
MY FATHER
PLANTED THE FALSE CONTENT.

12:09.099 --> 12:11.231
HE PAID JESSICA OFF.
I'M SURE OF IT.

12:11.231 --> 12:13.233
WHY?
 WE HAD A FIGHT.

12:13.233 --> 12:15.205
THE BASTARD SAID
HE WAS COMING AFTER ME.

12:15.205 --> 12:17.737
I SAID, "BRING IT."
 THAT WAS A RECKLESS MOVE.

12:17.737 --> 12:20.110
YEAH, WELL, I DIDN'T THINK I HAD
ANYTHING ELSE LEFT TO LOSE.

12:20.110 --> 12:22.212
IT SEEMS HE THOUGHT
OF ONE THING.

12:25.015 --> 12:28.248
DARLING, WE'RE LATE FOR
OUR MEETING WITH LIBBY WELLS.

12:28.248 --> 12:30.180
YEAH, I CALLED HER STUDIO
AND CANCELED THAT APPOINTMENT.

12:30.180 --> 12:32.022
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

12:32.022 --> 12:33.924
JIMMY BRENNAN?

12:33.924 --> 12:36.126
HEARD OF HIM?

12:36.126 --> 12:38.789
I HADN'T HEARD OF HIM, BUT
IF I'M TO BELIEVE WHAT'S
IN THIS POLICE REPORT,

12:38.789 --> 12:40.961
HE MAY ALSO GO BY
"DEAR OLD DAD."

12:41.962 --> 12:43.333
IT'S TRUE.

12:43.333 --> 12:45.996
MY FATHER SHOWED UP AT THE
ORPHANAGE THAT YOU DUMPED ME AT.

12:45.996 --> 12:48.768
INSTEAD OF BEING ALLOWED
TO SEE HIS SON, HE WAS
CITED FOR TRESPASSING.

12:48.768 --> 12:51.101
I GOT SHIPPED OFF TO A FAMILY
IN OHIO THE VERY NEXT DAY.

12:51.101 --> 12:53.373
WHOEVER GAVE YOU THIS
INFORMATION WANTED TO HURT YOU.

12:53.373 --> 12:55.005
WHO WAS IT?

12:55.005 --> 12:56.907
WAS IT NOLAN?
 YOU KNOW WHAT?
I'LL ASK THE QUESTIONS HERE.

12:58.909 --> 13:01.211
WHEN DID YOU MEET HIM?
 WHEN I WAS 15.

13:01.211 --> 13:03.183
WAS HE YOUR BOYFRIEND?
 NO.

13:03.183 --> 13:04.414
WE WERE TOGETHER ONCE.

13:07.017 --> 13:09.019
THERE ARE 32 JIMMY BRENNANS
IN THE TRI-STATE AREA.

13:09.019 --> 13:11.822
I'M HOPING ONE OF
THEM'S MINE. TAKE A LOOK.

13:14.424 --> 13:17.928
HE WAS NOT A FATHER,
NOT THE KIND YOU DESERVED.

13:17.928 --> 13:19.569
[ SLAMS TABLE ]
 YEAH, WELL,
YOU KNOW WHAT?

13:19.569 --> 13:21.401
THAT'S MY DECISION
TO MAKE.

13:30.040 --> 13:32.412
DANIEL? WHY AM I LEARNING
FROM BITSY HOPKINS,

13:32.412 --> 13:35.285
WHO HEARD FROM HER MAID, THAT
YOU HAVE A FRIEND STAYING OVER,

13:35.285 --> 13:37.487
ONE WHO SIPS CHAMPAGNE
AT MY SWIMMING POOL?

13:37.487 --> 13:40.851
I REALLY DON'T CARE WHAT
SOME OLD BAT FROM ACROSS
THE ROAD IS SAYING,

13:40.851 --> 13:43.593
NOT WHEN MY OWN FATHER IS
TRYING TO SUE ME INTO OBLIVION.

13:43.593 --> 13:46.056
YES, I'M AWARE,
AND I'M HERE IF YOU NEED ME.

13:46.056 --> 13:48.428
YOU'RE POKING
A DANGEROUS BEAR, THOUGH.

13:49.860 --> 13:51.531
I CAN HANDLE DAD.

13:51.531 --> 13:54.034
I'M TALKING
ABOUT EMILY.

13:54.034 --> 13:57.307
SHE'S WAGING PSYCHOLOGICAL
WARFARE ON THIS FAMILY.

13:57.307 --> 13:59.870
YOU ARE FOOLISHLY TAUNTING HER
WITH YOUR INFIDELITY.

13:59.870 --> 14:02.012
WELL, AFTER THE HELL
THAT BITCH HAS PUT ME THROUGH,

14:02.012 --> 14:03.874
SHE DESERVES TO HAVE
HER NOSE RUBBED IN IT.

14:03.874 --> 14:05.876
IT'S A FINE STRATEGY
IF IT'S JUST THE TWO OF YOU,

14:05.876 --> 14:08.478
BUT YOU BROUGHT SARA
ONTO THIS BATTLEFIELD.

14:08.478 --> 14:11.882
SHE IS A SOFT TARGET.
EMILY WILL CRUSH HER.

14:11.882 --> 14:15.025
I KNOW BECAUSE I DISMANTLED
CONRAD'S FIRST WIFE

14:15.025 --> 14:17.027
IN A SIMILAR MANNER.

14:17.027 --> 14:18.528
WELL, I APPRECIATE
THE CONCERN,

14:18.528 --> 14:20.260
BUT I'LL DISMANTLE MINE
 MY WAY,

14:20.260 --> 14:22.262
LIMB BY LIMB.

14:30.270 --> 14:33.974
NOTHING LIKE A LITTLE RETAIL
THERAPY. SORRY FOR THE MESS.

14:33.974 --> 14:36.446
YEAH, YOU'LL BE
CLEANING IT UP YOURSELF.

14:36.446 --> 14:38.308
I FIRED THE STAFF.

14:38.308 --> 14:39.950
WHAT?

14:39.950 --> 14:42.452
"WHAT?"
[ SCOFFS ]

14:42.452 --> 14:45.385
GRAYSON DIRTY LAUNDRY IS GETTING
AIRED THROUGH THE MAID CHAIN.

14:45.385 --> 14:48.418
I QUESTIONED THE SERVANTS,
AND WHEN NO ONE STEPPED FORWARD,

14:48.418 --> 14:50.890
I HAD TO AXE
THE WHOLE TEAM.

14:50.890 --> 14:52.923
THAT WASN'T FAIR,
DANIEL.

14:52.923 --> 14:55.465
FOR 25 YEARS,
NOT A SINGLE EMPLOYEE

14:55.465 --> 14:57.928
VIOLATED THEIR
CONFIDENTIALITY AGREEMENTS.

14:57.928 --> 15:00.630
NOW SUDDENLY THEY'RE GOSSIPING
BECAUSE SARA SPENT THE NIGHT?

15:00.630 --> 15:02.632
[ CHUCKLES ] GOD.

15:02.632 --> 15:05.375
THE FACT THAT YOU STILL THINK
I'M AN IDIOT MAKES ME LAUGH.

15:05.375 --> 15:08.178
DO YOU WANT TO KNOW
WHAT I REALLY THINK, DANIEL?

15:08.178 --> 15:13.513
I ASK MYSELF OVER AND OVER
AGAIN, "WHY DID HE CHEAT?"

15:13.513 --> 15:16.116
AND LET'S BE HONEST --
WE BOTH KNOW YOU STRAYED

15:16.116 --> 15:18.118
LONG BEFORE YOU LEARNED
THE TRUTH ABOUT ME

15:18.118 --> 15:20.290
ON OUR WEDDING NIGHT.

15:20.290 --> 15:23.593
WHAT MADE YOU
LOSE INTEREST, HUH?

15:23.593 --> 15:26.596
I'M NOT DOING ALL OF THIS
BECAUSE I'M A BORED HOUSEWIFE.

15:26.596 --> 15:29.659
I'M FIGHTING
TO WIN YOU BACK.

15:32.332 --> 15:34.204
REALLY?

15:34.204 --> 15:37.367
I'VE BEEN RUMINATING
ON YOUR POWERS OF DECEPTION,

15:37.367 --> 15:40.540
AND I REALIZED
THAT EVERYTHING YOU SAY

15:40.540 --> 15:44.674
IS HIDDEN BEHIND FAKE CONCERN
OR A PHONY SMILE.

15:44.674 --> 15:48.418
IN FACT, IF ANYTHING ELSE
SUSPICIOUS HAPPENS AROUND HERE,

15:48.418 --> 15:50.420
I'LL KNOW
YOU'RE BEHIND IT.

15:50.420 --> 15:54.024
AND JUST LIKE TODAY, OTHER
PEOPLE WILL PAY THE PRICE

15:54.024 --> 15:56.256
UNTIL YOU FINALLY REALIZE

15:56.256 --> 16:00.290
THAT THERE'S NO PLACE FOR YOU
IN MY LIFE AND YOU LEAVE.

16:00.290 --> 16:02.292
[ SIGHS ]

16:12.672 --> 16:15.345
Patrick:
IS THAT HIM?

16:15.345 --> 16:16.646
Boy: DAD!

16:16.646 --> 16:18.478
Jimmy: HEY, KIDDO!
HOW YOU DOING?

16:18.478 --> 16:20.180
GRRRR!

16:20.180 --> 16:23.313
OKAY, KIDDO, GO!
GO! HERE! BOOM!

16:23.313 --> 16:26.656
WHY HAVE YOU NEVER ASKED ME
ABOUT MY ADOPTIVE FAMILY?

16:28.388 --> 16:31.491
THE ONLY WAY I COULD
SURVIVE LETTING YOU GO
WAS TO IMAGINE YOU HAPPY.

16:31.491 --> 16:35.295
WELL...
HERE'S THE REALITY.

16:35.295 --> 16:38.598
ED AND BARBARA OSBOURNE
WERE MY PARENTS.

16:41.431 --> 16:44.034
I-I DON'T REALLY, UH,
REMEMBER MUCH ABOUT HER.

16:44.034 --> 16:47.107
SHE DIED WHEN I WAS 4.

16:47.107 --> 16:51.441
AND AFTER THAT,
DAD MARRIED ANNE.

16:54.684 --> 16:58.248
ANNE DIDN'T GIVE A DAMN
ABOUT ME, SO...

16:58.248 --> 17:00.190
NEITHER DID HE.

17:02.492 --> 17:05.555
TO FEEL THAT KIND OF
REJECTION FROM YOUR --

17:05.555 --> 17:08.328
YOUR FATHER
MAKES YOU FEEL LIKE, UM...

17:10.200 --> 17:12.262
IT MADE ME FEEL LIKE THERE
WAS SOMETHING WRONG WITH ME...

17:12.262 --> 17:13.403
NO...

17:13.403 --> 17:15.365
SOMETHING, UH...

17:17.237 --> 17:20.569
SOMETHING BAD,
UNLOVABLE.

17:24.544 --> 17:26.376
I STILL DO.

17:28.448 --> 17:30.220
OH, NO! HE'S COMING IN!
HE'S COMING IN!

17:30.220 --> 17:34.053
WHICH WAY -- OHH! I GOT HIM!
HE'S GONNA SLAM HIM! BOOM!

17:34.053 --> 17:36.786
IT COULD HAVE
BEEN DIFFERENT.

17:40.360 --> 17:42.592
[ MAN WOLF-WHISTLES ]

17:43.733 --> 17:46.236
HI. IT'S SO GOOD
TO SEE YOU.

17:46.236 --> 17:48.568
MM. YOU TOO.

17:48.568 --> 17:50.740
YEAH, I WOULD HAVE
STOPPED BY SOONER,

17:50.740 --> 17:53.403
BUT I HAD TO MAKE SURE
THAT PATTY CAKES

17:53.403 --> 17:55.375
AND HIS MOMS
WERE OFF-SITE.

17:55.375 --> 17:59.109
DAMN, GIRL. WHAT IS
WITH ALL THE ZEROES?

17:59.109 --> 18:01.381
DANIEL TRIED TO
PUT ME IN MY PLACE

18:01.381 --> 18:03.813
BY FIRING
THE HOUSE STAFF TODAY.

18:03.813 --> 18:07.357
THE LEAST I CAN DO IS COVER
THEIR SALARIES...AND THEN SOME.

18:07.357 --> 18:10.120
YOUR HUSBAND'S...
KIND OF A HOLE.

18:10.120 --> 18:12.662
HE EVEN HAS
SARA SLEEPING OVER.

18:12.662 --> 18:14.624
[ SCOFFS ]
 HE'S TRYING TO
CHASE ME AWAY.

18:14.624 --> 18:17.497
YOU KNOW, WITH THE LEVERAGE
THE GUY'S GUNPLAY GAVE YOU,

18:17.497 --> 18:20.099
IT'S NOT LIKE HE CAN JUST
ASK FOR A DIVORCE.

18:20.099 --> 18:22.332
IT'S A RISK
THAT HE JUST MIGHT TAKE.

18:22.332 --> 18:26.306
HE LOVES SARA,
SO SARA'S GOT TO GO.

18:26.306 --> 18:29.479
MM, ANOTHER DAY,
ANOTHER BREAKUP.

18:31.681 --> 18:34.284
YOU'RE NOT EVEN
GONNA ASK ABOUT AIDEN?

18:35.715 --> 18:38.748
HOW IS HE?
 HE'S ONE OF THE REASONS
I WANTED TO STOP BY.

18:38.748 --> 18:41.120
I MEANT WHAT I SAID.
WE CAN'T BE TOGETHER.
 NO, NO, NO.

18:41.120 --> 18:43.393
I'M NOT HERE
ON HIS BEHALF.

18:43.393 --> 18:45.395
[ SIGHS ]

18:45.395 --> 18:47.497
I WANT TO
CUT HIM LOOSE, TOO.

18:47.497 --> 18:51.501
I ONLY LET HIM STAY WITH ME
BECAUSE YOU ASKED ME TO.

18:51.501 --> 18:54.334
BUT NOW WITH NIKO
IN THE PICTURE

18:54.334 --> 18:58.568
MAKING BIG BEN CHIME
 EVERY HOUR ON THE HOUR, UGH,

18:58.568 --> 19:01.641
THEY NEED TO FIND
THEIR OWN LOVE SHACK.
 THEY'RE TOGETHER?

19:03.343 --> 19:06.176
YOU DIDN'T KNOW?
I DIDN'T REALIZE...

19:06.176 --> 19:07.347
[ SIGHS ]

19:07.347 --> 19:08.678
WHERE ARE YOU GOING?

19:08.678 --> 19:11.181
I JUST -- I CAN'T
SIT STILL ANY LONGER.

19:26.866 --> 19:28.638
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

19:31.801 --> 19:33.803
[ EXHALES SHARPLY ]

19:42.912 --> 19:44.514
[ HEART BEATING ]

19:48.358 --> 19:50.890
[ DISTORTED NOISE ]

19:54.394 --> 19:56.226
Man: [ Echoing ]
EMILY?

19:57.627 --> 19:58.628
EMILY?

20:02.502 --> 20:03.503
EMILY?

20:12.542 --> 20:15.445
WHAT ARE YOU DOING HERE?

20:25.455 --> 20:26.526
Aiden: EMILY?

20:27.827 --> 20:29.859
WHAT'S GOING ON?

20:31.931 --> 20:35.305
I-I WAS LOOKING
FOR NOLAN.

20:37.367 --> 20:39.369
ARE YOU OKAY?

20:41.010 --> 20:44.013
YOU...
YOU SEEM UNSTEADY.

20:44.013 --> 20:48.618
OH, JUST, UH,
SINCE MY HEAD INJURY...

20:48.618 --> 20:51.621
I'M GETTING A LITTLE DIZZY
SOMETIMES. IT'S -- IT'S NOTHING.

20:51.621 --> 20:54.854
I NEED TO GET HOME. I-I HAD
NO INTENTION OF SEEING YOU.

20:54.854 --> 20:56.926
NO. YOU WAIT. I'VE GOT
THINGS TO SAY TO YOU.

20:56.926 --> 20:58.788
I CAN'T HAVE THIS
CONVERSATION RIGHT NOW.

20:58.788 --> 21:01.431
LOOK, I UNDERSTAND YOU
GOT HURT, BUT YOU DON'T
JUST GET TO ABANDON ME

21:01.431 --> 21:02.832
WITHOUT HEARING
MY SIDE OF THINGS.

21:02.832 --> 21:05.795
LOOK, I CAN'T FORGET ABOUT
THE FUTURE WE PLANNED TOGETHER.

21:05.795 --> 21:07.997
OKAY? AND NEITHER CAN YOU. W-WHY
ELSE WOULD YOU BE COMING HERE,

21:07.997 --> 21:10.770
GIVING ME MIXED SIGNALS?
YOU'RE CONFLICTED.
 NO, I'M NOT.

21:10.770 --> 21:12.271
IF YOU WALK OUT OF HERE,
THIS IS OVER.

21:12.271 --> 21:13.943
YOU'RE GONNA HAVE TO LIVE
WITH YOUR CHOICE.

21:13.943 --> 21:16.045
LIKE YOUR CHOICE
TO SCREW NIKO?

21:16.045 --> 21:17.947
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

21:26.356 --> 21:29.319
WE KNOW IT WAS YOU
WHO PLANTED THE MISINFORMATION.

21:29.319 --> 21:30.990
FIRST LIBEL, NOW SLANDER?

21:30.990 --> 21:33.463
I WOULD WATCH MY WORDS
IF I WERE YOU, MS. LeMARCHAL.

21:33.463 --> 21:36.926
CUT THE CRAP, DAD. ONLY
YOU WOULD MALIGN YOURSELF
JUST TO SCREW ME OVER.

21:36.926 --> 21:38.898
OKAY.
HOW DO WE FIX THIS?

21:38.898 --> 21:42.071
I'M WILLING TO DROP MY SUIT
JUST AS SOON AS YOU FIRE MY SON.

21:42.071 --> 21:44.033
WHAT ARE YOU
TRYING TO PULL?

21:44.033 --> 21:46.606
JUST SOMETHING
THE FRENCH CALL A COUP D'ETAT.

21:46.606 --> 21:49.579
MY SOURCES INFORM ME
THAT THERE'S A CLAUSE
IN DANIEL'S CONTRACT

21:49.579 --> 21:52.742
THAT ALLOWS YOU TO BUY BACK
HIS SHARES IN VOULEZ.

21:52.742 --> 21:54.914
I WOULD, IN TURN,
PURCHASE THEM FROM YOU

21:54.914 --> 21:56.746
AT TWICE THE MARKET VALUE.

21:56.746 --> 21:58.618
IF YOU THINK WE'RE GONNA CAVE
TO YOUR THREATS, YOU HAVE --

21:58.618 --> 22:00.490
I'LL DO IT.

22:01.651 --> 22:02.652
MARGAUX.

22:02.652 --> 22:05.395
THIS IS NOT
ABOUT NEGOTIATING.

22:05.395 --> 22:09.328
HE'S OUT TO DESTROY YOU,
AND I WON'T ALLOW MY SUCCESS

22:09.328 --> 22:12.962
OR MY FAMILY'S REPUTATION
TO BE KILLED IN THE CROSSFIRE.

22:14.904 --> 22:17.507
YOU WANT TO GET IN BED
WITH THE DEVIL?

22:17.507 --> 22:18.968
CLEARLY,
I CAN'T STOP YOU.

22:24.914 --> 22:28.448
I ASSUME SATAN
WILL WANT THE CORNER OFFICE.

22:28.448 --> 22:31.020
I HAVE NO DESIRE
TO PUNCH A CLOCK --

22:31.020 --> 22:32.852
JUST MY BOY.

22:36.656 --> 22:39.859
WHAT IS THIS?

22:41.030 --> 22:42.392
WHERE'S AIDEN?

22:43.393 --> 22:44.894
I DON'T KNOW.

22:44.894 --> 22:47.967
WE WERE SUPPOSED
TO HAVE DINNER, BUT HE'S GONE.

22:47.967 --> 22:51.441
NO CALL,
NO TEXT, JUST GONE.

22:51.441 --> 22:53.903
DOESN'T IT BOTHER YOU
WHEN PEOPLE ARE INCONSIDERATE?

22:53.903 --> 22:57.647
YEAH...
NIKO, IT DOES.

22:57.647 --> 22:59.809
AND, UH...
[ SCOFFS LIGHTLY ]

22:59.809 --> 23:03.753
LOOK, WHILE I WAS
HOPING TO CHEW THIS FAT
WITH YOUR BOO PRESENT,

23:03.753 --> 23:06.916
UH, I THINK IT'S TIME I JUST
RIPPED OFF THE BAND-AID.

23:10.920 --> 23:15.495
O...M-G.

23:15.495 --> 23:18.868
I'M STUDYING MY FATHER'S AUTOPSY
FOR THE FIRST TIME.

23:18.868 --> 23:23.903
THE AUTHORITIES WERE UNCLEAR
AS TO THE MURDER WEAPON,

23:23.903 --> 23:26.776
BUT THOSE STAB WOUNDS
TELL A TALE.

23:26.776 --> 23:29.779
THEY WERE MADE BY
A KATANA -- HIS KATANA.

23:29.779 --> 23:32.512
HOW CAN YOU BE SO SURE?

23:32.512 --> 23:36.045
BECAUSE IT TRAVELED
EVERYWHERE WITH HIM AND
NOW IT'S NOT IN HIS LOFT.

23:36.045 --> 23:39.949
I THINK
THE KILLER STOLE IT.

23:39.949 --> 23:44.454
AND I WILL HUNT HIM
TO THE ENDS OF THE EARTH.

23:46.095 --> 23:50.930
IN THE MEANTIME, I'M PRACTICING
SEPARATING SKIN FROM FLESH.

23:54.063 --> 23:55.605
WAS THERE SOMETHING
YOU WANTED TO SAY TO ME?

23:55.605 --> 23:58.738
IT CAN WAIT.
 OKAY.

24:03.643 --> 24:05.475
Sara: YOU'RE HOME!

24:05.475 --> 24:08.618
I HAVE A SURPRISE.

24:08.618 --> 24:12.982
I STOPPED BY YOUR FULL GOURMET
KITCHEN FOR A SNACK EARLIER.

24:12.982 --> 24:17.086
NOBODY WAS THERE,
SO I STARTED PUTTERING AROUND,

24:17.086 --> 24:20.660
AND NEXT THING
YOU KNOW...

24:20.660 --> 24:23.593
♪ USED A CALLING CARD
AT THE PAY PHONE ♪

24:23.593 --> 24:25.565
EVERYTHING'S FROM SCRATCH.

24:25.565 --> 24:27.597
CAPRESE SALAD,
PASTA PRIMAVERA,

24:27.597 --> 24:29.769
AND PISTACHIO GELATO
FOR DESSERT.

24:29.769 --> 24:32.972
AND AFTER DINNER,
OUR ITALIAN THEME CONTINUES

24:32.972 --> 24:35.144
WITH "ROMAN HOLIDAY"
IN THE SCREENING ROOM.

24:37.847 --> 24:39.909
WHY, YOU'RE VERY SWEET.

24:41.881 --> 24:43.553
WHAT'S WRONG?

24:43.553 --> 24:46.185
MY FATHER HAD ME
OUSTED FROM VOULEZ.

24:46.185 --> 24:50.690
[ SIGHS ]
DANNY...

24:50.690 --> 24:52.892
WHAT'S GOING ON
LATELY, HUH?

24:52.892 --> 24:54.924
JUST SEEMS LIKE
YOU CAN'T CATCH A BREAK.

24:56.025 --> 24:57.827
ARE YOU KIDDING ME?

24:57.827 --> 25:00.199
I JUST CAUGHT
THE BIGGEST BREAK OF MY LIFE --

25:00.199 --> 25:01.901
YOU.

25:01.901 --> 25:04.904
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

25:04.904 --> 25:07.006
I DON'T KNOW. I-I-I JUST CAN'T
BE IN THIS HOUSE RIGHT NOW.

25:07.006 --> 25:08.978
EVERYTHING
REMINDS ME OF HIM.

25:08.978 --> 25:11.781
OKAY, WELL, LET'S GO OUT.
ANYWHERE YOU WANT.

25:11.781 --> 25:13.813
OKAY...

25:13.813 --> 25:15.214
ITALY.

25:15.214 --> 25:16.616
SERIOUSLY?

25:18.017 --> 25:20.650
UH, WHAT ABOUT KEEPING UP
APPEARANCES FOR YOUR MARRIAGE?

25:20.650 --> 25:21.791
WHAT ABOUT EMILY?

25:21.791 --> 25:23.122
I DON'T CARE ABOUT
EITHER OF THOSE THINGS.

25:23.122 --> 25:26.726
TOMORROW, YOU AND I
ARE GONNA HOP ON THE JET

25:26.726 --> 25:28.728
AND TAKE A ROMAN HOLIDAY
OF OUR OWN.

25:29.799 --> 25:30.930
[ LAUGHS ]

25:30.930 --> 25:34.904
COME ON.
[ CHUCKLES ]

25:37.937 --> 25:40.940
♪♪♪

25:40.940 --> 25:43.212
[ INDISTINCT TALKING ]

25:51.180 --> 25:53.853
YOU SHOULDN'T
HAVE FOLLOWED ME HERE.

25:53.853 --> 25:57.086
WELL, AFTER I SAW YOU
STEAL AWAY FROM THE HOUSE,
YOU LEFT ME NO CHOICE.

26:01.060 --> 26:04.033
THOSE GUYS OVER THERE
WORK FOR JIMMY.

26:05.264 --> 26:08.638
I, UH, CALLED
HIS CONSTRUCTION COMPANY

26:08.638 --> 26:09.969
PRETENDING TO BE A ROOFER
LOOKING FOR A JOB.

26:09.969 --> 26:12.171
IT WASN'T HARD TO FIND
HIS FAVORITE WATERING HOLE.

26:12.171 --> 26:14.003
ALL RIGHT, BEFORE YOU MAKE
CONTACT WITH THAT MAN,

26:14.003 --> 26:16.045
THERE ARE THINGS I HAVE TO
TELL YOU ABOUT HIM.

26:16.045 --> 26:17.607
I DON'T REALLY
WANT TO HEAR IT.

26:17.607 --> 26:19.008
THERE HAVE BEEN TOO MANY TIMES
SINCE WE'VE RECONNECTED

26:19.008 --> 26:20.780
THAT YOU'VE PUNTED
THIS CONVERSATION.

26:22.111 --> 26:24.153
I WANT TO MEET
MY FATHER ON MY TERMS,

26:24.153 --> 26:27.086
NOT THROUGH
YOUR IMPRESSIONS OF HIM.

26:27.086 --> 26:29.018
SO, PLEASE...

26:31.120 --> 26:32.992
...JUST GO.

26:37.296 --> 26:38.928
Man: EXCUSE ME.

26:47.136 --> 26:48.908
YOU...

26:48.908 --> 26:51.080
RELAX, HONEY.

26:52.882 --> 26:55.084
[ GASPS ]

26:56.786 --> 27:00.249
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

27:00.249 --> 27:02.251
HEY.
 [ GASPING ]

27:02.251 --> 27:05.054
IT'S OKAY. SHH, SHH!
IT'S OKAY.
 TAKE ME OUT OF HERE,
PLEASE.

27:05.054 --> 27:07.927
COME ON.
LET'S GO, COME ON.

27:12.201 --> 27:13.663
THANK YOU.

27:24.343 --> 27:28.277
DID YOU KNOW, DEEP DOWN,
I HATE TEA?

27:28.277 --> 27:30.379
[ CHUCKLES SOFTLY ]

27:30.379 --> 27:32.882
MY MOTHER WAS A FAN
OF INSTANT COFFEE.

27:32.882 --> 27:37.226
SHE WAS A VULGAR WOMAN
WHO MURDERED HER LOVER

27:37.226 --> 27:41.030
WHEN I WAS 15 AND FORCED ME
TO TAKE THE BLAME.

27:41.030 --> 27:44.163
WHEN I RELEASED BACK
TO HER CUSTODY...

27:46.095 --> 27:49.068
SHE STOOD BY AS ANOTHER ONE
OF HER BOYFRIENDS...

27:50.069 --> 27:52.872
...MOLESTED ME.

27:52.872 --> 27:55.044
AFTER SHE THREW ME OUT,

27:55.044 --> 27:58.908
I MADE MYSELF DRINK
FORTNUM'S EARL GREY

27:58.908 --> 28:03.252
AS A WAY TO FORGET ABOUT MY PAST
AND SEEM MORE UPPER-CRUST.

28:03.252 --> 28:05.254
[ CHUCKLES ]

28:06.285 --> 28:08.257
WHAT DID JIMMY BRENNAN
DO TO YOU?

28:10.790 --> 28:13.793
WELL, AS I TOLD YOU,
HE LIVED DOWN THE HALL.

28:13.793 --> 28:17.126
I WAS A CHILD
PRETENDING TO BE AN ADULT,

28:17.126 --> 28:19.869
DESPERATE
TO RE-CREATE MYSELF.

28:19.869 --> 28:24.173
JIMMY WAS LIKE A BIG BROTHER,
A FEW YEARS OLDER THAN I,

28:24.173 --> 28:27.807
AND HE ALWAYS
WATCHED OVER ME.

28:27.807 --> 28:30.709
SO, WHEN A FUSE BLEW
ONE DAY IN MY APARTMENT,

28:30.709 --> 28:33.813
I DIDN'T THINK TWICE
ABOUT FOLLOWING HIM
DOWN TO THE BASEMENT

28:33.813 --> 28:36.115
TO HELP HIM FIX IT.

28:39.949 --> 28:45.955
HE KISSES ME...AND I SAY,
"NO, WE'RE JUST FRIENDS,"

28:45.955 --> 28:48.858
AND I TRY TO PULL AWAY.

28:48.858 --> 28:52.731
AND HE HAS THIS LOOK
ON HIS FACE LIKE A MONSTER.

28:53.803 --> 28:56.005
HE PUNCHES ME,

28:56.005 --> 28:59.839
AND I RAISE MY ARMS
TO COVER MY FACE

28:59.839 --> 29:01.841
TO MASK MY SHAME
AND MY CONFUSION,

29:01.841 --> 29:03.973
BECAUSE I HAD
WORKED SO HARD.

29:03.973 --> 29:06.876
I DID EVERYTHING
TO CHANGE MYSELF, AND I...

29:09.378 --> 29:12.751
I KNEW HE COULD
STILL SEE THE VICTIM.

29:13.953 --> 29:16.886
AND HE PUSHES MY FACE
INTO THE COLD CONCRETE

29:16.886 --> 29:20.289
AND HE WHISPERS,
"RELAX, HONEY."

29:22.531 --> 29:25.364
OVER AND OVER AND OVER.

29:28.267 --> 29:31.841
A-ALL I COULD DO...

29:31.841 --> 29:36.806
WAS FOCUS ON THE PILOT LIGHT
UNDERNEATH THE WATER HEATER...

29:40.209 --> 29:43.182
...AND WAIT FOR HIM TO BE DONE.

29:46.916 --> 29:50.119
THE DAY YOU WERE DELIVERED,
THEY PUT YOU IN MY ARMS

29:50.119 --> 29:53.392
AND YOU HEARD MY VOICE AND
YOU LOOKED STRAIGHT IN MY EYES.

29:54.493 --> 29:57.396
AND I FELT THIS CALM.

29:59.298 --> 30:01.300
THERE WAS NOTHING
OF JIMMY IN YOU.

30:01.300 --> 30:03.933
YOU WERE FROM ME
AND NO ONE ELSE.

30:06.375 --> 30:08.207
AND WE WERE HAPPY.

30:08.207 --> 30:10.139
THEN WHY DID YOU, UM...

30:10.139 --> 30:13.342
HE STARTED STALKING ME,
SO WE, UH...

30:15.985 --> 30:18.587
WE RAN FROM
APARTMENT TO APARTMENT

30:18.587 --> 30:20.890
UNTIL THERE WAS
NOWHERE ELSE TO GO.

30:23.853 --> 30:27.296
AND THEN
THIS MIRACLE HAPPENED --

30:27.296 --> 30:30.259
A SCHOLARSHIP TO PARIS.

30:32.831 --> 30:34.333
PAINFUL AS IT WAS,

30:34.333 --> 30:36.505
I KNEW IT WAS THE ONLY WAY
I COULD PROTECT US BOTH.

30:37.967 --> 30:40.469
WHEN I TOOK YOU
TO SISTER REBECCA,

30:40.469 --> 30:44.874
I TOLD HER THAT JIMMY
MIGHT COME FOR YOU,

30:44.874 --> 30:47.516
AND SHE VOWED TO KEEP YOU AWAY
FROM HIM AT ANY COST.

30:50.980 --> 30:52.982
[ CRYING ]

30:56.085 --> 30:57.957
[ SIGHS, SNIFFLES ]

30:59.989 --> 31:01.430
[ Voice breaking ]
THE TRUTH...

31:04.063 --> 31:07.036
I DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT TO DO WITH IT.

31:09.098 --> 31:12.171
WITHHOLDING IT FROM YOU
CAUSED SUCH ANGUISH.

31:14.944 --> 31:19.278
BUT HOW COULD REVEALING IT
NOT CAUSE YOU MORE?

31:25.915 --> 31:27.586
PATRICK.

31:29.218 --> 31:31.991
DO NOT LET
THESE CIRCUMSTANCES

31:31.991 --> 31:34.893
DEFINE YOU THE WAY
I LET THEM DEFINE ME.

31:38.527 --> 31:41.270
[ SMOOCHES ]
 [ SNIFFLES ]

31:42.501 --> 31:44.033
HEY.

31:44.033 --> 31:45.574
HEY.

31:45.574 --> 31:47.606
HOW'S THE MAGAZINE?

31:47.606 --> 31:50.439
YOU SORT OUT HOW THOSE LIES
GOT IN THERE?

31:50.439 --> 31:52.411
STILL SORTING.
 YEAH?

31:52.411 --> 31:54.913
I WOULD RATHER NOT BORE YOU
WITH THE DETAILS.

31:54.913 --> 31:57.046
I'M JUST GLAD TO BE HOME.

31:57.046 --> 32:01.220
WELL, I'M GLAD
THAT YOU FEEL THIS IS HOME.

32:01.220 --> 32:03.993
WHAT IS ALL THIS?
 I'VE BEEN HOUSE HUNTING.

32:03.993 --> 32:06.625
WHERE WILL YOU MOVE TO?

32:06.625 --> 32:09.959
IDEALLY, UM,
SOMEPLACE CLOSE...

32:09.959 --> 32:13.262
WITH A YARD, UM...

32:13.262 --> 32:15.704
WITH YOU.

32:20.669 --> 32:23.942
YOU'VE SAID THAT YOU LOVE
WAKING UP WHERE WE ARE.

32:23.942 --> 32:25.574
WELL...

32:28.077 --> 32:29.948
I LOVE YOU.

32:29.948 --> 32:33.482
AND I KNOW IT SEEMS SUDDEN,
BUT IF I'VE LEARNED ANYTHING,

32:33.482 --> 32:36.986
IT'S THAT LIFE IS TOO SHORT
AND HAPPINESS IS FLEETING.

32:36.986 --> 32:38.988
I THINK THAT
WE MAKE A GREAT TEAM,

32:38.988 --> 32:42.331
AND A HOME --
A REAL HOME --

32:42.331 --> 32:46.335
SHOULD BE SOMEPLACE
THAT WE START TOGETHER.

32:51.740 --> 32:55.244
SAY SOMETHING. I'M SWINGING
FOR THE FENCES HERE.

32:56.375 --> 32:58.207
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

32:58.207 --> 33:00.579
I LOVE YOU, TOO.

33:09.018 --> 33:12.621
THIS WAS TAKEN BY
A BANK SECURITY CAMERA

33:12.621 --> 33:15.324
ACROSS FROM YOUR FATHER'S LOFT
THE NIGHT OF HIS MURDER.

33:15.324 --> 33:16.765
WHO IS HE?

33:16.765 --> 33:18.297
GREGOR HOFFMAN,

33:18.297 --> 33:20.999
THE ONE WHO PLANTED THE BOMB
AT GRAYSON GLOBAL LAST YEAR.

33:20.999 --> 33:24.002
YOUR FATHER WAS ONTO HIM.
I THINK HOFFMAN REALIZED IT.

33:24.002 --> 33:27.106
I REACHED OUT TO MY
CONTACTS, AND ONE CAME
BACK WITH A CELLPHONE PING,

33:27.106 --> 33:29.378
PROVING THAT HOFFMAN
IS ALIVE AND WELL

33:29.378 --> 33:31.710
AND LIVING IN MOSCOW.

33:31.710 --> 33:34.443
SO, I GOT YOU A FLIGHT.

33:35.444 --> 33:37.446
IT LEAVES TONIGHT.

33:39.488 --> 33:41.150
YOU'RE NOT COMING WITH ME.

33:43.652 --> 33:47.696
MY FATHER TRAINED YOU
TO BE WHAT YOU ARE TODAY.

33:47.696 --> 33:50.359
YOU LOVED HIM.
YOU --

33:54.203 --> 33:57.566
BUT YOU LOVE EMILY MORE.

33:59.037 --> 34:00.639
COME ON.

34:01.770 --> 34:04.643
I'LL TAKE YOU TO NOLAN'S.
YOU CAN PACK.

34:06.715 --> 34:09.248
WHATEVER WE NEED,
WE'LL BUY WHEN WE GET THERE,

34:09.248 --> 34:11.350
INCLUDING THE LUGGAGE
TO BRING IT ALL HOME.

34:11.350 --> 34:13.581
HEY, HOW ABOUT ONE OF THOSE
LOUIS VUITTON TRUNKS?

34:13.581 --> 34:17.485
OH, IT'S ITALY.
I'M GOING GUCCI, BABY.

34:17.485 --> 34:20.159
[ CHUCKLES ]

34:20.159 --> 34:22.261
SARA MARIE.

34:24.663 --> 34:27.696
MA.
WE, UM...

34:27.696 --> 34:29.768
H-HOW ARE YOU HERE?

34:29.768 --> 34:31.840
WELL, WHEN YOU REFUSED
TO ENGAGE WITH ME, SARA,

34:31.840 --> 34:33.842
I DIDN'T KNOW
WHAT ELSE TO DO.

34:33.842 --> 34:35.643
[ SIGHS ]

34:35.643 --> 34:36.705
SO, THIS IS
WHERE YOU'VE BEEN

34:36.705 --> 34:39.648
WHEN YOU TELL ME
YOU'RE AT WORK?

34:39.648 --> 34:42.281
YOU'RE LYING
TO YOUR FAMILY,

34:42.281 --> 34:45.313
SNEAKING AROUND
WITH THIS...PRINCE?

34:45.313 --> 34:46.655
IF I COULD
JUST EXPLAIN --
 YOU DON'T TALK TO ME.

34:48.117 --> 34:51.389
NOW, I DON'T KNOW
HOW YOU MANIPULATED

34:51.389 --> 34:54.123
MY SMART,
SELF-SUFFICIENT GIRL,

34:54.123 --> 34:57.266
BUT I WON'T FORGET
THE HELL YOU PUT HER THROUGH,

34:57.266 --> 34:59.228
AND I DID NOT NURSE YOU
BACK TO HEALTH

34:59.228 --> 35:01.200
TO SEE YOU
BECOME THIS PERSON,

35:01.200 --> 35:04.673
THIS HOME-WRECKER.
 NO, IT'S NOT LIKE THAT.
DANNY AND I LOVE EACH OTHER.

35:04.673 --> 35:06.575
SO YOU CAN DO
WHATEVER YOU WANT?

35:06.575 --> 35:09.738
SHE ALMOST DIED, AND HERE
YOU ARE, MOVING IN ON HER MAN.

35:09.738 --> 35:11.810
THAT GIRL IS SNOWING YOU.
SHE'S A MENACE.

35:11.810 --> 35:13.682
SHE RUINED DANNY'S LIFE.

35:13.682 --> 35:14.883
NO, OUR PROBLEMS
DIDN'T START

35:14.883 --> 35:16.885
UNTIL YOU CAME BACK
INTO HIS WORLD.

35:20.289 --> 35:22.691
COME ON, SARA,
WE'RE LEAVING.

35:23.692 --> 35:25.354
MA.

35:32.431 --> 35:34.863
LOOK,
I LOVE YOU, BUT...

35:37.706 --> 35:39.908
YOU GOT TO MIND
YOUR OWN BUSINESS.

35:48.146 --> 35:51.480
YOU ARE NO LONGER
A DAUGHTER OF MINE.

35:56.225 --> 35:58.427
GOOD LUCK, SWEETHEART.

35:58.427 --> 36:00.789
I'M SORRY FOR YOUR PAIN.

36:04.533 --> 36:05.534
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

36:07.366 --> 36:09.368
COME HERE.
COME HERE.

36:30.419 --> 36:33.662
Sara: I'M SORRY
I MADE US MISS OUR FLIGHT.

36:33.662 --> 36:37.626
OH, THAT'S THE BEAUTY
OF FLYING PRIVATE.

36:37.626 --> 36:39.898
OUR DEPARTURE TIME
IS WHENEVER WE WANT.

36:41.470 --> 36:43.702
I, UH --
I WAS THINKING,

36:43.702 --> 36:46.435
I WANTED TO
REACH OUT TO YOUR MOM.

36:46.435 --> 36:49.808
I WANT TO EXPLAIN
OUR SIDE OF THINGS.
 YEAH, IT WON'T WORK.

36:49.808 --> 36:53.282
I'LL -- I'LL GET
A DIVORCE. I-I'LL PHONE
MY ATTORNEY TOMORROW --

36:53.282 --> 36:55.644
NO, EMILY IS NEVER
LETTING YOU GO, DANNY.

36:55.644 --> 36:57.716
SHE DESTROYED MY RELATIONSHIP
WITH MY MOTHER,

36:57.716 --> 36:59.588
AND THAT WAS JUST
HER FIRST SWING AT ME.

36:59.588 --> 37:01.350
THEN WE'LL SWING BACK.

37:01.350 --> 37:03.922
MY MOM WAS RIGHT.

37:03.922 --> 37:05.924
THIS ISN'T ME.

37:05.924 --> 37:10.799
I GOT SWEPT UP IN SOMETHING,
AND -- AND -- AND I WANT OUT.

37:29.278 --> 37:30.919
GOODBYE, DANIEL.

37:41.690 --> 37:43.732
MISSION ACCOMPLISHED?

37:43.732 --> 37:46.435
NIKO BOUGHT IT. SHE'S IN THERE
GATHERING HER THINGS.

37:46.435 --> 37:48.867
I HAVE TO ADMIT,
I'M SURPRISED YOU WERE WILLING

37:48.867 --> 37:50.699
TO DOCTOR
THAT INFORMATION FOR ME.

37:50.699 --> 37:53.342
[ CHUCKLES LIGHTLY ]

37:53.342 --> 37:55.374
YOU MEAN...

37:55.374 --> 37:58.507
SURPRISED THAT I WOULD HELP
COVER YOUR GUILT?

37:59.748 --> 38:01.380
AIDEN,
LIFE'S COMPLICATED,

38:01.380 --> 38:05.554
AS ARE THINGS
BETWEEN YOU AND EMILY.

38:05.554 --> 38:08.557
I AM WORRIED
ABOUT HER, ROSS.

38:08.557 --> 38:10.689
THE EMILY THAT LEFT ME
IS NOT THE ONE THAT I KNOW.

38:10.689 --> 38:12.461
SOMETHING IS OFF.

38:13.462 --> 38:14.993
REALLY?

38:16.695 --> 38:20.869
BECAUSE WHEN I SAW HER,
SHE SEEMED BACK TO NORMAL.

38:20.869 --> 38:23.432
[ LIQUID POURING ]

38:23.432 --> 38:25.033
WHAT DO YOU
THINK IS WRONG?

38:25.033 --> 38:27.576
I'M NOT CERTAIN.

38:27.576 --> 38:30.379
MAYBE YOU CAN GET TO THE BOTTOM
OF IT WHEN I'M OUT OF YOUR HAIR

38:30.379 --> 38:33.382
AND NIKO IS CHASING
HOFFMAN'S DEAD-END TRAIL.

38:34.483 --> 38:37.986
IT'S NOT A DEAD END.
SHE'LL FIND HOFFMAN.

38:37.986 --> 38:41.019
THAT WASN'T THE PLAN.

38:42.821 --> 38:44.993
THE MAN KILLED
DECLAN PORTER.

38:44.993 --> 38:48.827
YOU SAID YOU WANTED YOUR
FEMME NIKOTA TO TASTE VENGEANCE.

38:48.827 --> 38:53.031
WELL,
THIS WAY SHE WILL...

38:53.031 --> 38:55.333
AND JUSTICE WILL BE SERVED.

38:55.333 --> 38:58.066
STRAIGHT UP.
 [ MIKKY EKKO'S
"WE MUST BE KILLERS" PLAYS ]

38:58.066 --> 39:01.540
♪ I WOKE UP,
I WAS STUCK IN A DREAM ♪

39:01.540 --> 39:04.743
MANY BELIEVE THERE IS
NO SUCH THING AS TOO MUCH LOVE.

39:04.743 --> 39:08.447
♪ YOU WERE THERE,
YOU WERE TEARING UP... ♪

39:08.447 --> 39:11.720
THAT ITS WARMTH IS A COMFORT
 FROM WHICH WE NEVER TIRE.

39:13.452 --> 39:21.530
♪ BUT WE ALL KNOW
HOW TO FAKE IT, BABY ♪

39:21.530 --> 39:25.634
♪ AND WE ALL KNOW
WHAT WE'VE DONE ♪

39:25.634 --> 39:30.068
BUT WHEN LOVE TURNS TO
 OBSESSION, IT CONSUMES ITSELF.

39:31.470 --> 39:34.843
♪ CHILDREN OF THE WILD ONES ♪

39:34.843 --> 39:38.577
♪ KILLERS ♪

39:38.577 --> 39:41.580
♪ WHERE WE GOT LEFT TO RUN? ♪

39:43.482 --> 39:47.115
♪ CHILDREN OF THE WILD ONES ♪

39:47.115 --> 39:50.959
♪ CHILDREN OF THE WILD ONES ♪

39:50.959 --> 39:54.993
THE FLAME THAT NOURISHED
 BECOMES ANGRY, MERCILESS,

39:54.993 --> 39:57.566
AN ALL-CONSUMING BLAZE...

39:59.468 --> 40:01.900
♪ OOOH-OOOOH ♪

40:01.900 --> 40:05.133
...LEAVING US CONFUSED
 BY THE CHILL IN THE AIR

40:05.133 --> 40:07.706
AND THE HATE LEFT BEHIND.

40:10.639 --> 40:12.581
SARA LEFT ME.

40:12.581 --> 40:14.483
MM.

40:14.483 --> 40:16.515
IS THIS
WHAT YOU WANTED?

40:16.515 --> 40:17.946
TO BREAK ME?

40:18.747 --> 40:20.449
IS THIS WHAT YOU WANTED?!

40:20.449 --> 40:21.650
[ GRUNTING ]

40:21.650 --> 40:23.492
I TOLD YOU
I WAS GONNA FIGHT FOR US.

40:23.492 --> 40:26.194
ARE YOU INSANE?
THERE WILL NEVER BE AN US!

40:26.194 --> 40:28.557
THANKS TO YOU,
I'M DEAD INSIDE.

40:28.557 --> 40:31.530
SO AM I! WE DID THIS
TO EACH OTHER, DANIEL.

40:31.530 --> 40:34.903
YOU TOOK FROM ME, SO I TOOK
FROM YOU. DON'T YOU SEE?

40:34.903 --> 40:37.135
WE BELONG TOGETHER.

40:37.135 --> 40:38.737
UNH!

40:48.046 --> 40:50.849
STERILIZING YOU WAS
MY GIFT TO THE UNIVERSE.

41:01.830 --> 41:04.833
[ SNIFFLES, WHIMPERING ]

41:08.597 --> 41:11.600
[ EXHALES SHARPLY,
BREATHING HEAVILY ]

41:11.600 --> 41:15.574
[ HEART BEATING ]

41:15.574 --> 41:17.876
[ DISTORTED WARBLING ]

41:17.876 --> 41:21.850
[ PANTING ]

41:21.850 --> 41:23.852
[ HIGH-PITCHED NOISE,
WARBLING ]

41:26.885 --> 41:30.519
[ MAN WHISTLING
"ROW, ROW, ROW YOUR BOAT" ]

41:37.866 --> 41:39.868
OH, GOOD.
YOU'RE AWAKE.

41:45.934 --> 41:50.809
YOU WERE MARVELOUS
LAST NIGHT, MRS. GRAYSON.

41:50.809 --> 41:54.843
UNTIL OUR NEXT RENDEZVOUS.

41:57.746 --> 41:59.748
[ DOOR CLOSES ]

42:02.250 --> 42:04.222
HOW WAS THE FLIGHT
FROM CALIFORNIA?

42:04.222 --> 42:06.925
SMOOTH.
 IT'S FUNNY.

42:06.925 --> 42:08.597
WHEN THEY TOLD ME
WHO I WAS MEETING,

42:08.597 --> 42:10.528
I WAS EXPECTING TO SEE
THE FORMER GOVERNOR'S WIFE.

42:10.528 --> 42:13.001
HARDLY.
I'M THE FIRST MRS. GRAYSON.

42:13.001 --> 42:16.304
WELL, YOU KNOW WHAT THEY SAY --
NOTHING BEATS THE ORIGINAL.

42:17.305 --> 42:19.307
I THINK SO, TOO.
